{"tid":439413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"話說，一年前，「我」造左一本漫。","createTime":"2017-10-17T18:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T16:15:09.000Z","uid":145338,"like":65,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2ca20a8aa4faef6ff3ef96bf704e993ec3c0ca","tid":439413,"uid":145338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:55:35.000Z","msg":"話說，一年前，「我」造左一本漫。然後就拎去「原創誌交流展」度賣，果陣賣左三十零本。本來想今年畫埋個續集拎去參展，但係生活逼人，日日屈係屋企鳩造真係好SAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所想上黎集下氣希望大家比Ｄ鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n宜家就先POST第一集既內容等大家比Ｄ意見，之後會再POST埋宜家手上造緊既稿，大家睇就唔高興既就怒屌，睇得高興既就盛讚，「我」但求有人理下咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/024104_c5c9f044d03aec81277540cfa464cad3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F024104_c5c9f044d03aec81277540cfa464cad3.jpg&h=6816872e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/024113_12c9c282585f81b0c952b1ec071dd9c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F024113_12c9c282585f81b0c952b1ec071dd9c4.jpg&h=2b2cb2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/024116_71976b82c1c0ac94abedad9c8695372e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F024116_71976b82c1c0ac94abedad9c8695372e.jpg&h=ac9dbdea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/024118_f40589bbdbff6c1455b08b8455e7e706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F18%2F024118_f40589bbdbff6c1455b08b8455e7e706.jpg&h=0508e4d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/18/024119_d5e6ee2119bf60b058e